$gameSystem.addLog("みんなああいう感じじゃないんだ");

$gameSystem.addLog("松男はマジでバーテンダーやれよ");

\nc<>I noticed the fact that I had forgotten earlier during the
doujinshi event.
\nc<>Right now, I'm in a man's room late at night...
\nc<>The fact that we are alone, drinking alcohol.
\nc<>(Huh? This seems like a pretty dangerous situation...)

\nc<>During the live stream, it's fine if I don't become a

\nc<>That's not all. I didn't bring my smartphone because
there's a possibility of being identified, and no one knows
that 'Levantia' came here.
\nc<>In case something happens, no one will come to help.

\nc<>(...It should be fine. We're in the middle of a live
stream.)
(Besides, this alcohol doesn't have much
bitterness, so it should have a low alcohol content.)

\nc<>If you transform, your resistance to drugs will also
increase a little. Even if it's just beer, you'll get full

\nc<>Levantia was convinced that she wouldn't get drunk, let
alone get completely wasted.

\nc<>Yes, how about it? I would be happy if you could also give
me your impressions this time.

\nc<>Yes, it tastes slightly like caramel latte. But, it's much
sweeter than that--
\nc<>You can expect the next one. It's quite expensive.
\nc<>Can I really drink something like that?!

\nc<>Levantia, you can drink quite a bit, huh? Is it because you
have a lot of friends after all?

\nc<>Are you always going to drinking parties when you're not
transformed?
\nc<>Eh~ Do I really look like that? Hehe, *hiccup*...

\nc<>Levantia's face shot up at the sound of Matsuo's voice. Just
that alone made her head spin and feel dizzy.

\nc<>I couldn't understand even if I tried to think with my
broken head.

\nc<>Are you already drunk? You haven't even had 10 drinks yet.
Didn't they say magical girls are strong?
\nc<>I'm sorry. Huh...? This wasn't supposed to happen.

\nc<>Ah, I'm not blaming you. Don't push yourself. But, hmm...
it's a shame. I had something saved for the last.

\nc<>When I looked to the side, there were rows of bottles of
alcohol lined up. There were traces of about half of them
being drunk, but the rest hadn't even been opened.

\nc<>Levantia couldn't help but open her mouth, wondering if it
was her fault that the plan had gone off track again due to
her guilt.

\nc<>Are you okay? I'm so glad! Thanks to you, I was saved,
really.

\nc<>But it seems impossible to drink right away. Let's take a
break for a bit and then do it.

\nc<>I was just about to take a break. Levantia expressed her
gratitude while leaning against something, but quickly
changed to a question.

\nc<>The reason why Kei was drawn to the place was not the sofa,
but their chest.

\nc<>Moreover, before they knew it, Matsuo's hand was placed on
Levantia's thigh.

\nc<>Levantia can't help but feel a sense of crisis when she
comes this far.
\nc<>This kind of thing... it's better to keep some distance.

\nc<>It's fine, it's fine. This level of physical contact is
normal, right? Isn't that right, everyone?

\nc<>The chat was filled with questions as Matsuo asked. Although
there were some differences, the majority of the responses
affirmed Matsuo's words.

\nc<>Of course, it was because Levantia couldn't see Matsuo's
hand stroking her thigh from the listener's side, but she
wasn't in a state where she could notice it.

\nc<>It's difficult to ignore the flow that the majority has
created, even if you feel that something is off. Especially
if you're drunk.
\nc<>In the end, Levantia ended up allowing Matsuo's hand.
\nc<>They didn't know that it was just the beginning.

\nc<>During the break, let's have some small talk. By the way,
Levantia, do you have a boyfriend?
\nc<>No, I don't have one. I've never had one before.

\nc<>You've never had one before? That's surprising. Especially
since you're so cute. Ah, could it be that you went to an
all-girls high school?
\nc<>Yes, well... that's the kind of feeling...

\nc<>Even though she allowed it, whether she could ignore it or
not was a separate issue. Throughout the conversation,
Levantia's attention was constantly focused on her thighs.

\nc<>Matsuo's hand moves from stroking to squeezing,
transitioning from the outside of the thigh to the space
between the legs, becoming more and more bold.

\nc<>Just spreading my fingers now feels like it's hitting the
entrance of my vagina.

\nc<>Even though it should have been disgusting to have a man
touch her body, Levantia, who was drunk, didn't feel any

\nc<>Whenever Levantia became aware that it was actually the work
of a man, she felt a throbbing heat.

\nc<>Once you start to become aware, other things come into view
as well.

\nc<>Thick hands that are completely different from mine. Thick
arms wrapped around me from behind.
\nc<>They realized that all of it belonged to a strong male.

\nc<>Matsuo's arm didn't budge even when Levantia tried to gently
push away from his chest, despite being late.

\nc<>Rather, they had no choice but to become aware of the
situation they were in.

\nc<>It's dangerous if things continue like this.
I don't
know what exactly is dangerous, but it's dangerous
nonetheless.

\nc<>Levantia tried to pull Matsuo's hand away, following that
instinct.

\nc<>Matsuo's hand slipped between Levantia's legs before
anything else.

\nc<>Levantia, who was already drunk and completely wasted,
suddenly faced an unexpected situation, causing her thoughts
to come to a halt and freeze in place.

\nc<>If that's the case, there's nothing to get in the way.

Matsuo's hand easily slipped inside Levantia.
\nc<>What are you...!? Hey, sto- ah, stop...!

\nc<>Levantia tried to squeeze her thighs, but Matsuo's hand had
already slipped inside.

\nc<>If it's Levantia's pelvis to begin with, even if you squeeze
her thighs, there will still be a gap.
\nc<>Are you okay? In the first place, it's you who...

\nc<>Levantia, who was trying to get worked up, turned her gaze
to the screen upon hearing Matsuo's words. On the screen,
chat messages from curious viewers kept popping up one after
another.

\nc<>It's better to laugh quickly, don't you think? Or is it that
you want it to be revealed that you got wet from being
fingered?
\nc<>Is it still okay for a righteous magical girl?

\nc<>The source of a magical girl's power is the positive

\nc<>Even if you were labeled as a pervert in front of a large
crowd, would you still be able to use your powers properly?

\nc<>No way. Before talking about power, I should be too
embarrassed to even stand in front of people.

\nc<>If only I could have been pushed away by force. My drunken
body wouldn't listen to me.

\nc<>If I fail to control my strength, the sight of a magical
girl attacking someone will be broadcasted.

\nc<>In a situation where everything would only turn out for the
worst, Levantia could only choose the lesser of two evils,
which was still worse than the worst.

\nc<>I-It's nothing. I-I got a little drunk... and it seems like
I misunderstood something...

\nc<>Oh, you're way more drunk than I thought. Should we save
the leftover alcohol for next time?

\nc<>The fact that I got drunk is a kind of excuse. When Levantia
laughed and tried to cover it up, the chat box was filled

\nc<>After feeling relieved that they somehow managed to get
through it, their relief was short-lived as Matsuo's hand

\nc<>Matsuo's touch became even bolder than before. As if it were

honey pot.

\nc<>The stimulation that Levantia couldn't help but be aware of
since her thighs were being touched. When it was actually
given, her body received it as pleasure.

\nc<>Well then, let's try ranking the drinks we've had so far.
Levantia-chan, which one do you like? This one? Or this

\nc<>Ugh... I don't like either of them.

\nc<>So, liking someone or something like that... hyaah!?
\nc<>Oh, it looks like this is a hit.

\nc<>Levantia thought it was dangerous to continue like this.
They half-heartedly hid under the table as if trying to

\nc<>If I do that, at least I can hide my facial expressions and

\nc<>Of course, it was also a matter of abandoning the shield

\nc<>The faint sound, like static, mixed in between Matsuo's

\nc<>How many times have we repeated this? As the viewers
gradually began to mix their voices with doubts,

\nc<>Levantia quietly, but surely, reached climax while

\nc<>Ah, Levantia, you're completely exhausted, huh? Let's end

$gameSystem.addLog("今日レヴァちゃん女にしてやろうぜ");

\nc<>No way, I wouldn't do something like that. I'll make sure

\nc<>Well then, everyone, in the next stream-- Who is it? Who

\nc<？？？>Please open the door! I am Levantia's manager!

\nc<>That was close, ... I mean, look, the manager came to pick

\nc<>So, I'm saying it's not like that.
$gameSystem.addLog("魔法少女にもマネージャーとかいんのか");

\nc<>Well, today's stream ends here. Let's meet again in the

\nc<>I obtained the proof ticket Matsuo A-1.
